## Repo Notes
- Rust 2024 edition.
- Embedded model mappings live in `src/models.toml` via `include_str!`.
- Skills live in `.skills/`; files starting with `_` are partials.
- Frontmatter is YAML and optional; shared parsing lives in `src/skills.rs`.
- Avoid duplicating skill parsing/path logic; reuse shared helpers.
- Use `.j2` for Jinja templates (minijinja loads by name).

## Useful Commands
- `cargo build --release`
- `cargo test`

